      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>劳资纠纷阻碍贸易，加拿大下令港口重启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/canada-orders-ports-to-restart-as-labor-disputes-choke-trade-m3elw67s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府指示一个独立劳工委员会结束加拿大最大港口的停工，就像 8 月份对铁路部门采取的停工措施一样，以阻止该国经济陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/canada-orders-ports-to-restart-as-labor-disputes-choke-trade-m3elw67s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:27:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普获得更多时间寻求驳回纽约封口费案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-lawyers-get-more-time-to-argue-for-dismissal-of-ny-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鉴于选举结果，唐纳德·特朗普被给予一周的时间提出新的理由，以驳回其在纽约的封口费案，作为候任总统，他在就职前必须迅速解决一系列法律威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-lawyers-get-more-time-to-argue-for-dismissal-of-ny-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:03:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
